Multi selectors are separated by commas: **.list, #bat, #bar{** which can save you from having to repeat the same properties on each selector. **.list, #bat, #bar{
text-align:center;
filter:drop-shadow(0 0 4px #000)}** Sets center alignment and a drop shadow on all three.

